  <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>The U.S. has imitated Europe for years, boosting government spending and racking up debt, creating a health-care system that doesn’t work and adding costly new social benefits. Now it’s Europe’s turn to imitate the U.S. in profligacy.</p>
